      <section eId="sec_2445">
        <num>2445</num>
        <heading>Applicability</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_2445__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>conducts human\nresearch that is subject to and is in compliance with policies and\nregulations promulgated by any agency of the federal government for the\nprotection of human subjects, and</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_2445__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>conducts or proposes to conduct or\nauthorize human research, which is not subject to but does or shall\ncomply with federal policies and regulations, the commissioner may deem,\nsubject to conditions, such institution or agency's human research in\ncompliance with this article. Such attestation shall be submitted\nannually on or before January first to the department on a form\nprescribed by the commissioner.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
